abstract: They hold the fate of the party in their hands. And maybe not only their party.
snippet: They hold the fate of the party in their hands. And maybe not only their party.
lead_paragraph: Gail Collins: Bret, let’s get right to it. How do you want to see New Hampshire vote? Give me your ideal Democratic finish.

abstract: Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelenskiy dismissed his chief of staff Andriy Bogdan on Tuesday, cutting ties with a lawyer whose links with a prominent tycoon had made him one of Zelenskiy's most controversial appointments since taking office last year.
snippet: Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelenskiy dismissed his chief of staff Andriy Bogdan on Tuesday, cutting ties with a lawyer whose links with a prominent tycoon had made him one of Zelenskiy's most controversial appointments since taking office last ...
lead_paragraph: KIEV — Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelenskiy dismissed his chief of staff Andriy Bogdan on Tuesday, cutting ties with a lawyer whose links with a prominent tycoon had made him one of Zelenskiy's most controversial appointments since taking office last year.
headline_main: Ukraine's President Fires Chief of Staff After Reports of Turf War
headline_print_headline: Ukraine's President Fires Chief of Staff After Reports of Turf War

abstract: Joe Biden had spent much of the weekend ahead of New Hampshire's primary on Tuesday attacking his top Democratic presidential rivals when a young woman asked why voters should believe he could win a national election after his poor showing in Iowa.
snippet: Joe Biden had spent much of the weekend ahead of New Hampshire's primary on Tuesday attacking his top Democratic presidential rivals when a young woman asked why voters should believe he could win a national election after his poor showing in Iowa...
lead_paragraph: HAMPTON, N.H. — Joe Biden had spent much of the weekend ahead of New Hampshire's primary on Tuesday attacking his top Democratic presidential rivals when a young woman asked why voters should believe he could win a national election after his poor showing in Iowa.
headline_main: Biden Shows Tenderness and Temper on 2020 Presidential Trail
headline_print_headline: Biden Shows Tenderness and Temper on 2020 Presidential Trail

abstract: The “first in the nation” primary never lets Iowa tell it what to do. Especially not this year.
snippet: The “first in the nation” primary never lets Iowa tell it what to do. Especially not this year.
lead_paragraph: DERRY, N.H. — Throughout the nearly half century-long presidential rivalry between Iowa and New Hampshire, sometimes a state has to dig deep to make its case for why its contest is in fact superior.
